47.000Z","msg":"要令到一個制度失效，唔需要主動破壞個制度。<br />\n與之相反係要令到現有嘅制度滿足唔到當權者嘅利，最後當權者推翻自己設立嘅制度。<br />\n咁樣我哋反抗就會名正言順。<br />\n<br />\n所以我會投票，支持政府釋法同埋dq。<br />\n反正選舉完咗抗爭都會繼續"},{"pid":"743c7a6146407491270de6e26fc5911b7ed9437c","tid":1741976,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed13346c7755234938ea4086f44a3d5e3c236044","tid":1741976,"uid":195827,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a08f642b2153a6d729e9a5c8e0698debbc18aae9","tid":1741976,"uid":264797,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"你解決到人大釋法同DQ<br />\n我就去投票<br />\n<br />\n解決唔到 唔投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:29:58.000Z","msg":"自己主動放棄權利<br />\n就唔好怪人唔比人權你"},{"pid":"d3e411949cb4ae2edf6814c9f72113f63a6e8d6c","tid":1741976,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d3a20144add186a28376ffbe186f7b0cfdf0dc6","tid":1741976,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:42:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff2b06160ac05859ebeb52a73a1c7c86c3376d38","tid":1741976,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d76305433b1a37ecaed8420adb0a4db76e806008","tid":1741976,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c951031183d5ff390d6d0ba56edb80543cc6cfd","tid":1741976,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ff89a257da3927d228601245486130d9ed86c09","tid":1741976,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"絕殺共產黨大於一切"},{"pid":"f3461819d302b604665b36abfa9cfeb27e2d7750","tid":1741976,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"資源比咩人都好，我唔會睇紅<br />\n但就一撚定唔可以比保皇黨選到"},{"pid":"c5a3532